rComments: Great teacher. Engaging, energetic, and really interesting. From Texas A&M, pretty conservative, but very nice with a lot of patience. I hope to take another class with Prof McDowell again soon

Easy class. Gives 6 pop quizzes that you must read for and go to class every day. There is a short 5 page paper and a debate that takes up some time but overall isn't bad. The final is on-line and a joke if you have all of your notes together. Entertaining class, easy A if you put forth some effort.
